column4: If a mother figure appears in your dream, this is typically sign of the oedipus complex.
Father figures for males are associated with envy. For female, this signifies the electra complex.
If a mother figure appears in your dream, this typically sign of the oedipus complex.
Father figures if your a male as associated to envy. For female, this signifies the electra complex.
House represent the body. smooth, featureless buildings and male whilst featurfull ones with clingable objects are female.
Kings are the sign of a prosperous leader. It suggests you have the power to overcome obstacles.
Queens are ambigous their meaning is dependant on how they are represented in the dream.
Big animals are associated with dominance of the parents.
Freud interpreted that horses were symbolic of the father. Little Hans, a patient of Freuds, feared that the horse would castrate him as punishment for the incestuous desires towards his mother.
Visions of sea depend on its form. Calm seas reflect a good future. Rough seas show obstacles in your way. Perhaps you are going through the motions with someone?
Small animals represent children in dreams.
Vermin represent a resentment to children.
According to Jung, spiders represent shadows of ones personality, much like prey to a web.
Birth is almost always represented by some reference to water, indicating a mother-relationship to that person.
Seeds can represent a plan that was initiated and will grow. You should try discover the path to collect the fruits of this seed.
Freud believed journeys represent a willingness for death.
Clothes represents nakedness, typically by uniforms.
Nakedness is a sign you need to be less reliant on others.
The number three is a reference to your genetalia. You aren't being true to yourself.
